5.     Act

After demonstrating all the analysis and explaining how annual members and casual riders use Cyclistic bikes differently, it is time to suggest ways for converting casual riders into annual members.
Recommendation: Implement a new annual membership option that considers a cost-effective pricing model (monthly and annual plans), offering discounts and promotions to only members, and collaborate with local businesses (especially during the summer season and weekends) to attract casual riders to subscribe.

 
